  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\nNOTE: this wouldn't be fixed for now, but we should close the modal when the invite is done\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nWhen a user hits `Invite` multiple times to invite a contact to a community, the recipient sees multiple invites to the same community.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n- Create a Community\r\n- Invite a contact to join this community\r\n- Press invite again and again\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe recipient must only see this invite sent in once.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/95302135/161305440-e9369fc5-d75b-4e77-b010-c54b51312719.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Master :e26befb6c26141529a5c4263bc8b26aa7c27e042\r\n",
